<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,1369,1933]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[201,400,1585,1610]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Ecological notes.</emphasis>
Under rocks at the mouth of Cachoeira River (Ilhéus) (Almeida 
<emphasis box="[1131,1180,1585,1609]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">et al</emphasis>
